; qfasm2 input that assembles a 221-byte code segment.
;
; Concatenate after bootstrap/qfasm2.qf1 and bootstrap/qfasm-n221-ext.qf1.
; This proves the optional N221 ELF file-size path without loading a broad range
; table. The pseudo-instruction expands to 209 Nops followed by exit(42).

(Assemble (Program Start (Ins (Label Start) (Ins (BigExit42N221) End))))
